rows.label: qst201211_msg0003
rows.name: We did! Well? Look great, don't they?

rows.label: qst201211_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll have you know, cookies are
a cinch for someone like me!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0005
rows.name:
It would have gone smoother
if you didn't insist on
eyeballing the measurements...

rows.label: qst201211_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey, come on! You promised
you wouldn't tell!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh yeah, since you're already
here, how about you try one
and tell me what you think?

rows.label: qst201211_msg0012
rows.name:
No, you shouldn't! Don't joke about
that! And if you do, at least make
sure it's obvious you're joking!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0014
rows.name: Anyway, no poison there, so dig in!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0019
rows.name:
Delicious! They're
just how I like them!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0021
rows.name:
Great! Hear that, Seori? They're
passable! That's not half bad
for first time, eh? Eh?

rows.label: qst201211_msg0022
rows.name:
...That sense of self-satisfaction
will be a barrier to growth.

rows.label: qst201211_msg0023
rows.name:
Oh, give me a break. A little
praise never hurt anyone!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0025
rows.name:
Anyway, we got the go-ahead
as well now, so let's hand
out those Whelzaman Cookies!

rows.label: qst201211_msg0026
rows.name:
Exactly. Time to make the kids of
Fons Maim grin from ear to ear.
